<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Social Media - Home</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons+Round" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
    :root{
      --bg:#f5f4f0;--white:#ffffff;--ink:#111110;--muted:#6b6a66;
      --accent:#2563eb;--accent-light:#eff4ff;--border:#e4e3de;
      --shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);--shadow-lg:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    }
    body{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);min-height:100vh}
    nav{
      display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
      padding:0 2.5rem;height:60px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
      border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;
    }
    .nav-brand{
      font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.1rem;
      color:var(--ink);text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
    }
    .dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent)}
    .btn-pill{
      display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;padding:7px 16px;border-radius:100px;
      font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;
      border:none;transition:all 0.2s;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;
    }
    .btn-pill.primary{background:var(--accent);color:#fff}
    .btn-pill.primary:hover{background:#1d4ed8;transform:translateY(-1px)}
    .hero{max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;padding:5rem 2rem 3rem;text-align:center}
    .hero-badge{
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;
      background:var(--accent-light);color:var(--accent);
      padding:5px 14px;border-radius:100px;font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:600;
      margin-bottom:1.5rem;animation:fadeDown 0.5s ease both;
    }
    .hero-title{
      font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-weight:800;
      font-size:clamp(2.8rem,6vw,4rem);line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-0.04em;
      margin-bottom:1.2rem;animation:fadeUp 0.5s ease 0.1s both;
    }
    .hero-title .blue{color:var(--accent)}
    .hero-sub{
      font-size:1rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;
      max-width:440px;margin:0 auto 2.5rem;
      animation:fadeUp 0.5s ease 0.2s both;
    }
    .hero-cta{
      display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;
      animation:fadeUp 0.5s ease 0.3s both;
    }
    .btn-hero{
      display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:13px 26px;
      border-radius:14px;font-size:0.92rem;font-weight:600;
      cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;border:none;transition:all 0.25s;
      font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;
    }
    .btn-hero.primary{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.15)}
    .btn-hero.primary:hover{background:#222;transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.2)}
    .btn-hero.secondary{background:var(--white);color:var(--ink);border:1px solid var(--border)}
    .btn-hero.secondary:hover{border-color:var(--ink);transform:translateY(-2px)}
    .btn-hero i{font-size:1.1rem}
    .stats-row{
      display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:2px;
      margin:3rem auto 0;max-width:460px;
      background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      animation:fadeUp 0.5s ease 0.4s both;
    }
    .stat{flex:1;padding:1.2rem 1rem;text-align:center;border-right:1px solid var(--border)}
    .stat:last-child{border-right:none}
    .stat-n{font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:800}
    .stat-l{font-size:0.73rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px}
    @keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
    @keyframes fadeDown{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-10px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <a class="nav-brand" href="/"><span class="dot"></span>Social Media</a>
    <a href="/posts/" class="btn-pill primary">
      <i class="material-icons-round" style="font-size:1rem">grid_view</i> Ver posts
    </a>
  </nav>

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">
      <i class="material-icons-round" style="font-size:0.9rem">auto_awesome</i>
      Tu red social personal
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Conecta.<br>Comparte. <span class="blue">Explora.</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Publica tus ideas, descubre contenido de otros y gestiona tu perfil desde un solo lugar.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="/posts/" class="btn-hero primary">
        <i class="material-icons-round">grid_view</i> Ver publicaciones
      </a>
      <a href="/posts/new/<%= userId %>" class="btn-hero secondary">
        <i class="material-icons-round">add_circle_outline</i> Nuevo post
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="stats-row">
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n">🚀</div><div class="stat-l">Node.js</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n">🍃</div><div class="stat-l">MongoDB</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n">⚡</div><div class="stat-l">Express</div></div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>